V0705_01_00_00_0.text:
Hey, home skillet!
I'm Mimi Imimi!
Ready for today's test?

V0705_01_00_01_0.text:
Hi there! I'm Mimi!
And I'm totally into Rush Duels!

V0705_01_00_02_0.text:
Me and you! Rush Duel! Right now!
And I'm gonna win!

V0705_01_00_03_0.text:
You ready to boogie?
Then let's tear up the dance floor!

V0705_01_00_04_0.text: I'm surprised you showed up knowing I'm your opponent!

V0705_01_00_05_0.text: If you win, I'll give you coupons you can use at the mall!

V0705_01_00_06_0.text:
Cheeuh!
Of course I wanna Rush Duel!

V0705_01_00_07_0.text: One thing I'm not gonna do is lose to you!

V0705_01_00_09_0.text:
I have to Duel against my Yoshie!?
This is bogus!

V0705_01_00_10_0.text: If Yoshie thinks I'm his hero, I have to Duel like one!

V0705_01_00_12_0.text: If I win, you gotta hook me up with a VIP pass to your show!

V0705_03_00_00_0.text:
I used to shine back in my day...
And I still do!

V0705_03_00_01_0.text:
This is so fly!
I gotta keep the party goin'!

V0705_03_00_04_0.text:
This is bad!
As in bad bad, not good bad!

V0705_03_00_05_0.text:
I can't wig out!
Just gotta outwork 'em!

V0705_05_00_00_0.text: I'll break you before you break me!

V0705_05_00_00_1.text: This draw is gonna be the bomb!

V0705_07_09_00_0.text: The card I Set... is this!

V0705_07_09_01_0.text: I'll use the card I Set!

V0705_10_00_02_0.text: This is one Summon worth watching!

V0705_10_00_03_0.text: I bring nothing but the best!

V0705_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0705_11_03_00_0.text: I say see ya to my monster!

V0705_11_12_00_0.text: I'm gonna Fusion Summon a monster!

V0705_16_00_00_0.text:
I rule the dance floor!
Not you!

V0705_16_00_01_0.text:
You can't hang with me!
Toodles!

V0705_20_00_00_0.text: I'm Setting a card - and you don't know what it is.

V0705_21_00_00_0.text:
You should go home.
It's past your bedtime.

V0705_21_00_04_0.text: If we had a time machine, you'd know how rad I was!

V0705_21_00_05_0.text: Just gotta chill and survive 'til the next turn...

V0705_28_00_00_0.text:
That was phat!
I give the Duel a big thumbs up!

V0705_28_00_01_0.text: If I keep winning, I'll be president of Goha in no time!

V0705_28_00_02_0.text:
No one can stop me from climbing to the top!
Hahahaha!

V0705_28_00_03_0.text: Goha runs the world, and I'm gonna run Goha!

V0705_28_00_04_0.text: Not only will I keep my job, I might even get a promotion!

V0705_28_00_05_0.text: Parents work hard so that their kids can dream.

V0705_28_00_06_0.text: I get squished everyday in the subway when I go to work.

V0705_28_00_06_1.text:
And you seriously thought YOU could squish ME?
As if!

V0705_28_00_07_0.text: I remember your strategies from preschool.

V0705_28_00_08_0.text: Maybe I was too harsh on you.

V0705_28_00_09_0.text: You're allowed to Rush Duel after you finish your homework.

V0705_28_00_10_1.text: Fan club rules state I have to stay one Roa Radius away!

V0705_29_00_00_0.text:
My favorite soap opera's about to start.
Later skater!

V0705_29_00_01_0.text:
You flattened me like a pancake...
So not cool!

V0705_29_00_02_0.text: If I don't get better, I'll lose my job!

V0705_29_00_03_0.text: My dreams are fading away - like bleach on a stain!

V0705_29_00_04_0.text:
Is this for real?
You're this much better than me?

V0705_29_00_05_0.text: You might've pulled my petals, but I'm gonna bloom again!

V0705_29_00_06_0.text:
The sun's coming up...
Time flies when you're having fun.

V0705_29_00_07_0.text: The days when I was shining like a disco ball are over...

V0705_29_00_08_0.text: It's hard to keep up with the kiddies...

V0705_29_00_09_0.text: There's no parent who isn't proud to see their kid grow up.

V0705_29_00_10_0.text:
Oh no...
Am I a bad role model for Yoshie?

V0705_29_00_11_0.text: Roa's shining so bright that I have to wear sunglasses!

V0705_29_00_12_0.text:
Grrrrr!
You're not better than me!

V0705_33_00_00_0.text: The party's not over 'til I say it is!

V0705_30_00_00_0.text: That's a mature move you made.

V0705_30_00_01_0.text: I'm Number 6 of the Top of the Hexagon - elite of the elite!

V0705_30_00_02_0.text:
A heart this pure will help you fer sure!
The Mysterious M!

V0705_34_00_01_0.text: In a world of worker ants, I'm the queen!

V0705_34_00_02_0.text: The answer's somewhere in my 37 year-old brain...

V0705_34_00_03_0.text: Want these mega-rare Teacher of the Year trading cards?

V0705_34_00_04_0.text: Hide these ultra-rare cards in this ultra-rare paper bag.

V0705_34_00_05_0.text:
I love Italian food!
Just as much as my leg warmers!

V0705_34_00_06_0.text: I have a pet axolotl, but so does everyone, right?

V0705_34_00_11_0.text: When did you get that fantabulous card?

V0705_32_00_01_0.text:
Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links!
Give some dap to this app!

V0705_35_00_00_0.text:
I'm Mimi Imimi!
The secret to staying young... is a secret!

V0705_35_00_01_0.text: They invented the disco ball so I could groove!

V0705_36_00_02_0.text: Both Dueling and dancing's more fun when you have a partner!

V0705_36_00_03_0.text:
Gotta bounce for a sec.
You go!

V0705_36_00_05_0.text: You're not planning to ditch me, are you?

V0705_36_00_10_0.text:
Sigh...
I wanted to Duel with Roa longer...

V0705_36_00_12_0.text:
Sorry, Roa.
I don't deserve to be in your fan club.

V0705_08_00_00_0.text: I'll keep the party goin’ with the Spell, Party Party Party!

V0705_08_00_00_1.text: Nobody wants a step with no pep!

V0705_08_00_01_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Shining City Nights!

V0705_08_00_01_1.text: Now we’ll have a ball cuz all LIGHT monsters gain ATK!

V0705_08_00_02_0.text:
I activate a totally tubular Spell!
Triple Threat Thunder!

V0705_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Bubbleburst Shock!!

V0705_08_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Prison Island - Cell Block 5 & 6!

V0705_08_00_04_1.text: We both can't Tribute Summon Level 5 or 6 monsters!

V0705_08_00_05_0.text: The dance floor's getting too crowded!

V0705_08_00_05_1.text: I activate the Spell Card, Last Day of Beautiful Witch!

V0705_08_00_06_0.text:
You shouldn'tve upset me!
The Spell Card, Mother’s Rain!

V0705_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate the Spell, Dian Keto the Cure Master!
Heal me up!

V0705_08_00_08_0.text: I activate the Trap Card, Jewelry Trap Hole!

V0705_08_00_08_1.text: I'm kicking out a monster who wasn't on the guest list!

V0705_08_00_09_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Party Time - Disco Ball!

V0705_08_00_09_1.text: It brings my monster back to the dance floor!

V0705_08_00_10_0.text: I activate the Trap Card, Party Up!

V0705_08_00_10_1.text: It raises my LP equal to the attacking monster's ATK!

V0705_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Master's Cure!

V0705_08_00_12_0.text: I activate the Trap Card, Imprisoned Beautiful Witch!

V0705_08_00_13_0.text:
Your fun can't last forever! 
I play Bursting Your Bubble!

V0705_08_00_14_0.text: I activate the Trap Card, Mystery Handcuffs!

V0705_09_00_00_0.text: Dian Keto uses her effect to freshen me up!

V0705_09_00_01_0.text: I activate Dian Keto the Security Master's effect!

V0705_09_00_01_1.text:
Incardceration!
I send your card to the slammer and gain LP!

V0705_09_00_02_0.text: Dian Keto the Cooking Master activates her effect!

V0705_09_00_04_1.text: I return a monster in my Graveyard to my hand!

V0705_09_00_06_0.text:
Ring ring!
I activate Brick Phone Nyan Nyan's effect!

V0705_09_00_07_0.text: Fashion of Faith activates her effect!

V0705_37_00_00_0.text: This party is about to go crazy!

V0705_37_00_00_1.text: From the driving disco comes the queen of the boogie beat!

V0705_37_00_01_0.text: The party doesn’t stop ’til the sun comes up!

V0705_37_00_01_1.text: But when night turns to day, make way for the authority!

V0705_13_00_01_0.text: She locks up the fun to get the surveillance done!

V0705_37_00_02_0.text: You’re invited to the land of yum to calm your cravings!

V0705_37_00_02_1.text: This chef can cook up anything to tantalize your taste buds!

V0705_13_00_02_0.text: This master knows every dish in the recipe book!

V0705_13_00_02_1.text:
Let’s get cooking!
Dian Keto the Cooking Master!

V0705_13_00_06_0.text: Brick Phone Nyan Nyan's here to answer my call!

V0705_13_00_08_0.text:
Vice Jacker!
...Huh? When did I put this card in my deck?

V0705_19_00_00_0.text:
Dian Keto the Boogie Master!
Show 'em your moves!

V0705_19_00_01_0.text:
Go go go!
Dian Keto! Attack!

V0705_19_00_02_0.text: Dian Keto the Security Master attacks!

V0705_19_00_04_0.text: Dian Keto the Cooking Master attacks!

V0705_19_00_05_0.text:
Dian Keto the Cooking Master!
Turn 'em into stew!

V0705_19_00_12_0.text:
Kanan the Sword Diva!
Dance and slash!

V0705_19_00_14_0.text:
LaMoon the Party Princess!
Show 'em why you're VIP!

V0705_19_00_15_0.text:
Kanan the Security Guard!
Lock 'em up!
